<footer>
  <div class="container foot">
    <div>
      <div class="brand mb-06">
        <img src="/assets/img/logo.webp?v=1" alt="Logo Sentral Emas" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="28" height="28"/>
        <strong>Sentral Emas</strong>
      </div>
      <p class="my-02">Buyback aman via COD se‑Jabodetabek, mengikuti harga pasar hari transaksi. Transparan, cepat, dan terpercaya.</p>
